<plot>When Erma the busy oddball inventor cuts a man out of life, what's left behind is a big hole.. in the wall of her home! The incoming breeze awakens her dead grandmother who yells out: 'Go find a boy to fix that hole!' So when she makes a man, she soon finds that while she's chosen inventing over love, her invention is now a loving human...!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652751</url></doc>
